parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Seat Belt Latch and Retraction Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the seat belt latches and retraction mechanisms can lead to inadequate restraint of occupants in the event of a crash, increasing the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: Seat belts will not catch and lock
seat belts get caught under the backrest hinge
seat belts do not restrain occupants in a crash
seat belts tighten and won't release.
